data.description: Immaculate Turn Key End Unit villa in prime location gated Community of Las Verdes. Home features complete remodel in kitchen and baths. Gorgeous 42'' White Oak cabinets in the kitchen w/ large single sink. Both baths have new vanities, tops, fixtures and mirrors. Tiled throughout except master bedroom which is plush carpeting. Gorgeous light fixtures and fans complement the stylish arches leading to level finished family room. Full hurricane protection with Accordion Shutters on all windows and slider. Bose surround sound speakers built in. A delightful bright villa to call home for your new Florida lifestyle.
data.whatILove: Totally remodeled home with new kitchen and baths which include 42" White Oak kitchen cabinets, new countertops, appliances and vanity tops, plus beautiful 18" tile on the diagonal throughout living spaces and lush carpet in the master bedroom. Arched pass throughs to Family room adds nice architectural design to the home.
